<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Article Has Been Published</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #016934; /* Green */
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top-left-radius: 5px;
      border-top-right-radius: 5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #bf0a30; /* Red */
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #016934;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your Article Has Been Published!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{authorName}},</p>
    
    <p>We are pleased to inform you that your article <strong>"{{articleTitle}}"</strong> has been published in the Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy {{volumeInfo}}.</p>
    
    <div class="details">
      <p><strong>Article Title:</strong> {{articleTitle}}</p>
      <p><strong>Volume Information:</strong> {{volumeInfo}}</p>
      <p><strong>Publication Date:</strong> {{publicationDate}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Your valuable contribution to the field of social work and social policy in Africa is now available for readers worldwide.</p>
    
    <p>You can view your published article by clicking the button below:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{articleUrl}}" class="button">View Published Article</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>We encourage you to share your article with colleagues and on social media to increase its visibility and impact.</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for choosing the Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy for publishing your research.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The Editorial Team<br>
    Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© 2023 Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to you because you are an author with the journal. If you believe this was sent in error, please contact us.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
